# GitHub CODEOWNERS file
# Auto-assigns reviewers when files are modified in PRs
# Documentation:
# - https://help.github.com/articles/about-code-owners/
# - https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Syntax: pattern @user-or-team
# The last matching pattern takes precedence.

# Examples:
# *.md                    @doc-team
# /docs/                  @doc-team
# /.github/workflows/     @devops-team
# package.json            @security-team @maintainers

###############################
# Repository Default Owners
###############################
# Global fallback for all files
* @ruzickap
